Class BrowseInventoryFragment

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.ualberta.cmput301.t03.inventory.BrowseInventoryFragment

  • public class BrowseInventoryFragment

    Fragment that displays a ListView containing all Items from all friends. This can (later) be filtered by friends, category, and Texttual Query.
